a tornado that touched down in east mountain did some of the worst damage of friday's east texas twisters, damaging 25 houses, officials said. two mobile homes were destroyed in nearby glenwood acres
a tornado in gladewater extensively damaged the city hall, an elementary school, a car dealership, a supermarket and several mobile homes, while a funnel cloud that struck near mound city damaged a roof and overturned vehicles
